data.description: Welcome home to 223 Country Meadows Court! This beautiful ranch home is situated in a cul-de-sac and convenient to nearby Locust Grove. USDA area! This home has been well maintained with some updates. Living room with fireplace and open dining room. The kitchen has tons of storage! The spacious master suite includes a walk-in closet as well as a garden tub and separate shower. Large Laundry room/mud room area. There is an additional bonus room that can be used as a 4th bedroom, den, or office space with a separate entry/exit. Home sits on an open, spacious lot with a private backyard and patio area. Large outbuilding included.
